From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ming Zhangqun <north_sea@qq.com>
Date: Thu, 12 Jun 2026 16:00:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] add SPI flash vendor configs for usbplug

Add 11 missing SPI flash vendor configurations to rockchip-usbplug_defconfig.
These are needed for usbplug to recognize and initialize new SPI flash chips
in Maskrom mode. Without these configs, "获取 capability 失败" occurs when
using rkdevtool to flash new SPI flash chips.

Configs added: EON, ISSI, PUYA, FMSH, DOSILICON, BOYA, ZBIT, NORMEM, ATMEL,
SPANSION, STMICRO.

Signed-off-by: Ming Zhangqun <north_sea@qq.com>
---
 configs/rockchip-usbplug_defconfig | 11 +++++++++++
 1 file changed, 11 insertions(+)

diff --git a/configs/rockchip-usbplug_defconfig b/configs/rockchip-usbplug_defconfig
--- a/configs/rockchip-usbplug_defconfig
+++ b/configs/rockchip-usbplug_defconfig
@@ -72,8 +72,19 @@ CONFIG_SPI_FLASH=y
 CONFIG_SPI_FLASH=y
 CONFIG_SF_DEFAULT_MODE=0x1
 CONFIG_SF_DEFAULT_SPEED=50000000
 CONFIG_SPI_FLASH_GIGADEVICE=y
 CONFIG_SPI_FLASH_MACRONIX=y
+CONFIG_SPI_FLASH_EON=y
+CONFIG_SPI_FLASH_ISSI=y
+CONFIG_SPI_FLASH_PUYA=y
+CONFIG_SPI_FLASH_FMSH=y
+CONFIG_SPI_FLASH_DOSILICON=y
+CONFIG_SPI_FLASH_BOYA=y
+CONFIG_SPI_FLASH_ZBIT=y
+CONFIG_SPI_FLASH_NORMEM=y
+CONFIG_SPI_FLASH_ATMEL=y
+CONFIG_SPI_FLASH_SPANSION=y
+CONFIG_SPI_FLASH_STMICRO=y
 CONFIG_SPI_FLASH_WINBOND=y
 # CONFIG_SPI_FLASH_USE_4K_SECTORS is not set
 CONFIG_SPI_FLASH_MTD=y
